The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     IN THE CITY
                  
	 Milan Sangha beat Madarat AC 2-1 in the Officers Choice State Football League on Tuesday. Mithun Saha and Tarun Das scored for the winners while Seikh Raja pulled one back for Madarat AC.      
	RESULTS      
	Raiganj SC bt Baul Sporting Association 1-0; Globe Trotters SC bt NBSTC Rec. Club 4-2; Durgapur Steel Sporting bt Bolpore Town Club 2-0; Hirbandh FC lost to Manguria Basti Tiger Club 1-3; Mad- arat AC lost to Milan Sangha 1-2.                
	 An under-17 Twenty20 tournament, organised by the All India Cricket Research Institute, will be held at Victoria School and Goethals Memorial School ground in Kurseong from April 27 to May 4.       
	Teams from different schools and coaching centres will participate.                                                                                                                                                                     
